3.10	Genma_Saotome	List of Ranma ½ characters	Ranma ½ Ranma Nibun no Ichi, pronounced Ranma one-half) is a Japanese manga series written and illustrated by Rumiko Takahashi which was also adapted into an anime series. The story revolves around a 16-year old boy named Ranma Saotome who was trained in martial arts from early childhood. As a result of an accident during a training journey, he is cursed to become a girl when splashed with cold water, but hot water will change him back into a boy.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/b/b6/Ranma_Cast.jpg
